      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "っ……まだ匂うわね。朝から事務所内に\n蔓延しているこの油っぽい甘い香りはなんなのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "っ……まだ匂うわね。朝から事務所内に\n蔓延しているこの油っぽい甘い香りはなんなのかしら",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "いただきまーす！　もぐもぐ……はぁ～美味しいなぁ\n幸せだな～これでしばらくはドーナツ生活が出来そう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いただきまーす！　もぐもぐ……はぁ～美味しいなぁ\n幸せだな～これでしばらくはドーナツ生活が出来そう！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13966.6666667,
          "startTime": 35.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "（ああ、あそこで芽衣が大量のドーナツを広げていたのね）\n（気が付かれたら面倒だわ、ササッと通り過ぎましょう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（ああ、あそこで芽衣が大量のドーナツを広げていたのね）\n（気が付かれたら面倒だわ、ササッと通り過ぎましょう）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4000,
          "startTime": 37.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　mihoちゃんだ～！　打ち合わせ終わり？\nお疲れ様ー！　お腹空いてない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あ！　mihoちゃんだ～！　打ち合わせ終わり？\nお疲れ様ー！　お腹空いてない？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "（くっ……気が付かれてしまったわ……）\n（朝から何も食べてなくてお腹は空いているけれど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（くっ……気が付かれてしまったわ……）\n（朝から何も食べてなくてお腹は空いているけれど……）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "ねーねー！　お昼まだ食べてなかったら一緒に\nドーナツ食べない～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ねーねー！　お昼まだ食べてなかったら一緒に\nドーナツ食べない～？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。大丈夫よ。それにしても……\nその大量のドーナツ、一体どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ありがとう。大丈夫よ。それにしても……\nその大量のドーナツ、一体どうしたの？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "今日は芽衣の誕生日だからみんなが芽衣のために\n色んなドーナツをお取り寄せしてくれたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "今日は芽衣の誕生日だからみんなが芽衣のために\n色んなドーナツをお取り寄せしてくれたんだ～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツ博士の早坂芽衣でも初めて見るような\n激レアドーナツが沢山あるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ドーナツ博士の早坂芽衣でも初めて見るような\n激レアドーナツが沢山あるんだよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "見て見て～！　これは、さくらちゃんからもらった\n魚魚っとさん型の抹茶メロン味のドーナツでしょ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "見て見て～！　これは、さくらちゃんからもらった\n魚魚っとさん型の抹茶メロン味のドーナツでしょ～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "こっちの三角形のは、沙季ちゃんからもらった謎解き\nドーナツ！　謎を解くとドーナツの形が変化するんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "こっちの三角形のは、沙季ちゃんからもらった謎解き\nドーナツ！　謎を解くとドーナツの形が変化するんだよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9340.002505,
          "startTime": 101.1066691717
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "そう。良かったわね。それじゃ、私はもう行くわ\n今鳴ったのは私のお腹の音！？　芽衣には気付かれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そう。良かったわね。それじゃ、私はもう行くわ\n今鳴ったのは私のお腹の音！？　芽衣には気付かれ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あー、遙子ちゃんからもらった日本酒味のドーナツ\nとっても美味しいけど芽衣にはちょっと大人な味だな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あー、遙子ちゃんからもらった日本酒味のドーナツ\nとっても美味しいけど芽衣にはちょっと大人な味だな～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4666692098,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 17266.664123500006,
          "startTime": 129.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "誰か美味しく食べてくれる大人なお姉さんはいないかな\n半分に割って食べてるから安心だよ～。はいっ、どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "誰か美味しく食べてくれる大人なお姉さんはいないかな\n半分に割って食べてるから安心だよ～。はいっ、どうぞ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.63334198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……それじゃあお言葉に甘えていただこうかしら\nありがとう。あむっ……美味しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "くっ……それじゃあお言葉に甘えていただこうかしら\nありがとう。あむっ……美味しい……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8000086467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
